  }, "It was then the turn of Tughlaq and his gang of idiots. They moved national capitals around because they hated the weather."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
  }, "From somewhere, Babar, a descendant of a lame, one eyed king from Central Asia landed in India."), mdx("li", {
