  }, "YES")), mdx("p", null, "If you see, India is one of the very few countries to have a civilization which goes back to about 3000 BC. No other country has this big a history.\nTo put it in perspective, India\u2019s last golden age was in the 6th century BC. Wonder what were the others in the world doing at that time..."), mdx("p", null, mdx("span", _extends({
